T1	Intervention 566 1052	There were four randomised treatment phases, each of 4 weeks duration. The four blinded treatments were MPA 2.5 mg, MPA 5 mg, MPA 10 mg and matching placebo, taken for the last 14 days of each 28 day treatment cycle. CEE 0.625 mg was also administered once daily as open labelled tablets to all subjects throughout the study. Clinic BP was measured weekly with the mean values of weeks 3 and 4 of each phase used for analysis. Ambulatory BP was performed in the final week of each phase
